highlights.description: KC: A "really awesome glimpse of hope" that white Madisonians can talk about white privilege among themselves and understand it. Spoken by a woman of color. Would be useful to play for A group of white people who are wondering what white people can do about racism, or perceiving that white-only conversations are not useful for addressing racism
